0 M:N relationships in this schema' style='shape=note;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#fff2cc;strokeColor=#d6b656' vertex='1' parent='1'><mxGeometry x='2130' y='40' width='240' height='200' as='geometry'/></mxCell>
        <mxCell id='p1_participation' value='Participation summary from md
- Child/weak/archive entities are total participants
- USER/DOCTOR/SPECIALIZATION sides are usually partial
- CONTACT_QUERY and FEEDBACK_ENTRY are partial because nullable role FKs are allowed
- APPOINTMENT and PATIENT specializations are disjoint + partial
- CONTACT_QUERY specialization is disjoint + total' style='shape=note;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#fff2cc;strokeColor=#d6b656' vertex='1' parent='1'><mxGeometry x='2130' y='270' width='260' height='220' as='geometry'/></mxCell>
        <mxCell id='p1_standalone' value='Standalone physical tables
- ADMIN has no strong FK participation in the conceptual model
- TBLCONTACTUS is a legacy public form table kept separate from CONTACT_QUERY' style='shape=note;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#fff2cc;strokeColor=#d6b656' vertex='1' parent='1'><mxGeometry x='2130' y='520' width='260' height='130' as='geometry'/></mxCell>
